      "description": "This E46 M3 is a pristine example of BMW\u2019s engineering peak, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with crisp throttle response via six individual throttle bodies. The chassis remains structurally sound with documented subframe reinforcement, and the VANOS system has been professionally overhauled to ensure variable valve timing precision. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox to a tight M-variable differential. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, this specimen shows zero signs of typical wear, maintaining factory-spec compression and a leak-free undercarriage. It represents a turn-key investment for the discerning purist seeking analog performance.",
