      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines the standard for 'pre-owned.' This car is in showroom condition, having been meticulously garaged and pampered since day one. The exterior features a flawless, deep-gloss finish with absolutely zero swirls, chips, or imperfections; the paint depth remains consistent across every panel. Step inside to an interior that still carries that distinctive new-car scent\u2014the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, and the dashboard is free of any UV fading or micro-scratches on the trim. Mechanically, it is indistinguishable from a new unit, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. Every button, sensor, and feature functions with factory precision. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or discerning driver to own a piece of automotive perfection without the new-car depreciation. Professional inspections are welcomed and encouraged to verify the pristine nature of this vehicle.",
